{"type": "article", "id": 16714, "title": "歪嘴、大小眼…宜家这些蠢萌玩偶来自孩子的简笔画", "description": "“两只老虎，两只老虎，一只没有眼睛，一只没有耳朵，真奇怪…”", "date": "2015-10-28T15:35:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 17906, "name": "毛绒玩具"}, {"id": 17907, "name": "儿童教育"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}], "category": 18, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 17, "praise_count": 166, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605220300hbYEm3ktDTnS1IfX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t大小眼的蝙蝠<span>、</span><span>歪嘴的毛毛虫</span>（也有可能是蜥蜴，或者小恐龙）……宜家最新一批毛绒玩偶看起来有点特别，这些二维画风的设计实际上来自于儿童简笔画。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220255KkgdJnO1HCGU7eVB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t Thymeo，4 岁，比利时\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<strong><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220255WcgKJOPynAvE6t7o.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6171875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>宜家向全球年龄段在 </span><span>4 </span><span>岁</span><span>- 10 </span><span>岁的小朋友征集作品，最后从上千幅参赛者中选出了十名幸运儿，把他们的简笔画做成了量产的毛绒玩偶。</span><span>这批玩偶大多售价为 </span><span>3.99 </span><span>美元 </span><span>- 9.99 </span><span>美元间，销售所得的部分收入也将用作儿童慈善。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220256vRK1jhbAWlmwE2Io.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<b> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tKoen，10 岁，荷兰\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><span style=\"text-align:center;\"></span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220256tjLoYcFmEqdPgiGk.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.9578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tAlbert，7 岁，罗马尼亚\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220257A1OPg46Lri7uEzmU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tStella，6 岁，塞浦路斯\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220257MiXOnhZmkxqpw9A2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tMaja，8 岁和 John，5 岁，挪威 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220258KLTpnroO6l04XGW8.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tKarla，10 岁，克罗地亚\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220258l06kFTKV8I5u91wW.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tRosita，4 岁，加纳利群岛 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220259GpL03PQ529aEm1uj.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tDora，6 岁半，英国\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><span></span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220300UYDObRTfKhWI3wPm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tTerrence，6 岁，马来西亚\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<b><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605220300c197iabCMDTF8VB0.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> </b> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\tYou-Chen Wu，6 岁，中国台湾\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t自 <span>2003 </span>年起，宜家就与联合国儿童基金会联合发起了儿童教育项目，每卖出一个毛绒玩具或是儿童书，就捐出 <span>1 </span>欧元，捐献累积超过 <span>9,000 </span>万美元。<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t从下面这个视频中，你可以看到宜家是如何搜集儿童画作，然后从贴满了整个房间的画作中做出“艰难”的抉择，制作出几个玩偶版本进行比对，最后投入量产。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<iframe src=\"http://www.tudou.com/programs/view/html5embed.action?type=0&amp;code=HVi9HHa1_P0&amp;lcode=&amp;resourceId=380561142_06_05_99\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" frameborder=\"0\">\r\n\t</iframe>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}